as ever going to see his sheets, anyway?', 54, 0), (190820, 'We are turning against boys and forgetting a simple truth: that the energy, competitiveness, and corporal daring of normal, decent males is responsible for much of what is right in the world.', 17530, 0), (190821, 'Most men overestimate themselves. It’s the only way they can reproduce. It’s why we’re all here, us humans. Overestimation.', 30605, 0), (190822, 'I always knew he was selfish and self-indulgent and kind of lazy', 34797, 0), (190823, 'A man''s women folk, whatever their outward show of respect for his merit and authority, always regard him secretly as an ass, and with something akin to pity. His most gaudy sayings and doings seldom deceive them; they see the actual man within, and know him for a shallow and pathetic fellow. In this fact, perhaps, lies one of the best proofs of feminine intelligence, or, as the common phrase makes it, feminine intuition. The marks of that so-called intuition are simply a sharp and accurate perception of reality, a habitual immunity to emotional enchantment, a relentless capacity for distinguishing clearly between the appearance and the substance. The appearance, in the normal family circle, is a hero, a magnifico, a demigod. The substance is a poor mountebank.', 411, 0), (190824, 'Here is a piece of advice. Never pay attention to what a man says when he comes. Anything might be blurted out at that moment, and it rarely means anything.', 26959, 0), (190825, 'God will bless you and your marriage when you follow His blueprint.', 4239, 0), (190826, 'Men, we don''t need you in shining armor.We just need you a little bit brave, just a little bit brave.', 34798, 0), (190827, 'In many ways spiritual exercise is like physical exercise. If you stop exercising physically, your body may not show the results of inactivity for a while. But one day you wake up and find everything is sagging in all the wrong places.', 4239, 0), (190828, 'A Beautiful Woman Is A Baggage. Thank God