nto a desire and then and obsession!', 35012, 0), (191829, 'Most of the masses still believe in magic, you know. Spells. Potions. It''s a big business, I am told.', 1171, 0), (191830, 'I''ve finally decided to write about profit for a changeBut before I really started I already started to feel lameBaby what''s it to a beast who manely to money remains untamed', 230, 0), (191831, 'If there''s one lesson I can pass along to people in situations like mine, it''s that the best way to see a program through -- and it took me a long time to learn this -- is simply to accept the help, cooperate, and let others do what they think is worthwhile. In the meantime, continue racing to the finish line.', 35013, 0), (191832, 'Sales professional is a profession deals with people, it''s a people business not a selling job.', 12584, 0), (191833, 'the prudent business mind must not only think of competing with the prevailing giants in the market but must also not be oblivious of the latent deft of the masses who are yet to dare', 4606, 0), (191834, 'There is a mistake technical and scientific people make. We think that if we have made a clever and thoughtful argument, based on data and smart analysis, then people will change their minds. This isn''t true. If yoy want to change people''s behavior, you need to touch their hearts, not just win the arguments. We call this the Oprah Winfrey rule.', 4910, 0), (191835, 'Your Potential can far exceed your expectations', 26065, 0), (191836, 'A #GIRLBOSS knows when to throw punches and when to roll with them.', 5789, 0), (191837, 'Money amplifies what type of person you are in the world.', 35014, 0), (191838, 'Only move forward with creating a product that will be "above the bar.', 35015, 0), (191839, 'Don''t focus all your time and effort on creating the templates & perfecting the documents. Answering key product questions is more critical.', 35015, 0), (191840, 'Do not compromise on the quality and your customers will not negotiate on the price.', 589, 0), (191841, 'To find your way you must first take the steps', 35016, 0), (191842, 'Entrepreneur, if you''re going to start up, make sure you start up with excellence in mind', 24838, 0), (191843, 'If you believe that you''re doing will positive results, it will - even if it''s not immediately obvious.', 5789, 0), (191844, 'To be an ethical leader is indeed to be different. This kind of leader acknowledges the complexity of running a responsible business, yet tries to do it anyway.', 35017, 0), (191845, 'Entrepreneur, your last 20 tweets has to be about your brain, brand and business.', 24838, 0), (191846, 'To satisfy a want or a need, you must first go for it', 35016, 0), (191847, 'Reputation is an outcome; but it is also a valuable, strategic asset.', 35018, 0), (191848, 'It''s time to calculate your risks make amends to reduce errors and increase your successes', 35016, 0), (191849, 'Inspiring leadership communication is not about great oratory or great charisma; rather it is about getting others to believe in themselves and believe in your cause, and then achieve more than they thought was possible.', 35019, 0), (191850, 'Make project plan as simple as possible, but not simpler.', 19615, 0);
